<HEAD>U.S. Denies Visa to Soviet Film Curator</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CLEVELAND (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Soviet film curator was denied a visa to
attend a conference on cinema in the Soviet Union and the United
States, organizers said.
   Yuri Khodjaev, who oversees film festivals in Moscow, Leningrad,
Tashkent and other Soviet cities, was not granted a visa to come to
