<DATELINE>MILAN, Italy (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Thick fog enveloped central and northern
Italy for a sixth straight day Friday, forcing the cancellation of
dozens of flights and temporarily closing airports.
   Road traffic also was slowed by the fog, and several accidents
